1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,963
Nobody tells you this when you first start dirt biking.
刚开始玩越野摩托时，没人会告诉你这件事。

2
00:00:02,963 --> 00:00:05,431
The hard part is not about learning how to ride,
难的部分不是学会怎么骑车，

3
00:00:05,431 --> 00:00:07,900
it's actually finding somebody who gets it.
其实是找到一个懂这件事的人。

4
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:18,900
My first real ride was brutal, it was 100 degrees outside, I was sweating through everything, my legs were shaking, my hands were tired, and honestly I could barely stay on the bike.
我第一次真正的骑行非常残酷，外面37度，我浑身都被汗湿透了，腿在发抖，手也没了力气，说实话我几乎坐不住车了。

5
00:00:18,900 --> 00:00:22,533
But you know what the crazy thing is, I couldn't stop thinking about it.
但你知道疯狂的是什么吗，我一直忍不住想着它。

6
00:00:22,533 --> 00:00:26,167
That's when I realized dirt biking is addictive.
那时我意识到，越野摩托会让人上瘾。

7
00:00:26,167 --> 00:00:29,800
And it gets even better when you have somebody to share it to.
而当你有人可以分享时，它会变得更好。

8
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:36,800
However, most of what I found online felt scattered, outdated, or just not the way I wanted to be built.
然而，我在网上找到的大部分都感觉零散、过时，或者根本不是我想要的那种做法。

9
00:00:36,850 --> 00:00:42,130
So as a software engineer, I set out to do the one thing I know how. To build DirtBikeX
所以作为一名软件工程师，我决定去做我唯一会做的事。去打造 DirtBikeX

10
00:00:42,130 --> 00:00:48,289
myself. The kind of place I wish existed. It's got no bloat. You don't have to post
自己动手。我一直希望存在的那种地方。它没有臃肿的功能。你不用把同一个内容

11
00:00:48,289 --> 00:00:52,769
the same thing twice. 21 languages. All the good stuff.
发两遍。21种语言。所有好东西都有。

12
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:57,872
Most importantly, a real chance for us to be seen by fellow riders, so if you've been looking
最重要的是，我们真正有机会被同好骑手看见，所以如果你也像我一样，一直在寻找

13
00:00:57,872 --> 00:01:03,838
for dirt bike people like me, go and check out the invite code in the description. My name is Rubio
越野摩托伙伴，就去看看简介里的邀请码。我叫鲁比奥

14
00:01:03,838 --> 00:01:05,750
and I'll be waiting for you there!
我在那里等你！
